Valid value: internal_sql cloud_user_sql cloud_nouser_sql external_sql __++__internal_cmd_field_list

statement.description:
The Keywords of sql statement
Example: "join"

status.description:
The running status of sql statement
Valid value: Running, Success, Failed

The user name of who initiated the request
